            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the vegetables are in the oven, drain the <strong>tuna</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>drained tuna</strong> and <strong>oregano</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and set aside – this is your <strong>marinated tuna</strong></p>",
